{"tid":1323312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]721朝早照去金鐘 跟住開始 be water 轉場?","createTime":"2019-07-16T08:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T14:44:41.000Z","uid":84408,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"01944847ee29f1a783ce7537a71a9c8b58f34c7e","tid":1323312,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"第一 <br />\n金鐘呢加無鐵馬 放唔到陣<br />\n無嘢可攻可守<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n班狗由14年到呢加已經熟哂啲路<br />\n再出圍堵一齊仆街<br />\n沙田果日都已經有巴打分析咗係撓幸獲勝<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n金鐘無民居 空擴 出飛機大炮都得<br />\n人太集中 比人放大技一齊死<br />\n<br />\n我地目的係五大訴求<br />\n我地知道會有機會打交<br />\n但我地目的唔係為咗同狗打交<br />\n<br />\n有無考慮即日 be water做各區行動<br />\n<br />\n利申 夢遊者"},{"pid":"e32a478dc49d36b41752b34aade0c9fbe6bbfae5","tid":1323312,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"1ec2020a3dd6c0ceaf0cde0fd4a73882641e89e8","tid":1323312,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77bdc4343e3bc74e2b1fdbfb5b2cc790a5ace464","tid":1323312,"uid":84408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"預計當晚狗鐵基本不停金鐘<br />\n甚至灣仔中環<br />\n水路尖咀黑狗等緊你<br />\n小巴唔好諗<br />\n巴士嘅話都有機危險<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非通常尾班車就走八成因為驚走唔到<br />\n<br />\n但如果我地每區自己地頭開拖 <br />\n<br />\n就唔使考慮<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">走唔到</span></span> 同埋 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">運物資呢個問題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然人數上都會差好遠<br />\n<br 